    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment for COU1 is Accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors met or exceeded their required gradation levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is offset by the strong output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96) and the high relevance of the validation activities to the COU. The Equivalency of input parameters factor was reviewed and accepted based on documented traceability of model inputs to experimental measurements. The team judges the aggregate evidence sufficient to support use of the FEA model ensemble for the intended regulatory purpose.",
